Products.RichDescription:
Ingham’s Free Range Chicken Breast Garlic Butter Kievs with a Sourdough Crumb Mix.


Only the finest ingredients go into Ingham's Free Range Chicken Breast Kievs. Made using Australian free range chicken raised on local FREPA accredited farms, lightly coated in a rustic sourdough crumb mix then stuffed with garlic and butter for the perfect family dinner.

- Australian free range chicken raised on local farms.

- No artificial colours or flavours.

- Made with bone-in chicken breast.
